description:
This is my second album, in this i got togheter most of the finished tracks and projects i had since a year or so. Most of this stuff was posted on soundcloud and then deleted, and many WIPs have been posted too.

This is some kind of line in my productions. This is basically the line between my old and my new productions. After this i'm going to work alot on my projects and give my best to every track i will make.

There's a story to this album too, because it was originally going to be the soundtrack of an animation movie. I'll write the story for each songs in their respective descriptions when i get the time.

Thanks for listenning !

Too lazy to do it, but there's 18 tracks in this album, for a total of 1 hour and 9 minutes.
